    "description": "有史以来第一次，你可以让自己沉浸在一个铣削的世界里。<br><br>使用传统的铣削机来完成钻、铣、磨和切等操作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在自由铣削模式中，你可以导入自己的蓝图，从而制作出独特产品的样板。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在职业模式中，你可以比拼精确度和完成挑战性任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/42c83d7b920e790692daabab7bc41beb.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/42c83d7b920e790692daabab7bc41beb.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/42c83d7b920e790692daabab7bc41beb.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/cf23a1abbc93e04f33856fe19141c84f.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/cf23a1abbc93e04f33856fe19141c84f.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/cf23a1abbc93e04f33856fe19141c84f.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过选择材料和大小来定制符合你的需求的工件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/55698203abcb6cd1f02e56cdcd3eedc3.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/55698203abcb6cd1f02e56cdcd3eedc3.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/55698203abcb6cd1f02e56cdcd3eedc3.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在真实的物理机制和运动方式下完成所有工作。同时切记：你的切割工具可能会折断！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/1a3d5d322cc903c35aef0e3aaddbc6e5.poster.avif?t=1770390681\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/1a3d5d322cc903c35aef0e3aaddbc6e5.webm?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/1a3d5d322cc903c35aef0e3aaddbc6e5.mp4?t=1770390681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
